Class ButtonMenuActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz.GeneralMenuActivity
      • com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz.ButtonMenuActivity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EditTradeActivity, ProfileActivity

    public abstract class ButtonMenuActivity
extends GeneralMenuActivity
    An abstract class that can be utilized in other classes. This class is purely based around giving us a generalizable set of tools that we can easily put into another class for buttons and text. This is widely seen across our application- this particular arrangement of buttons and text.
